01:30.821 --> 01:32.483
Okay.

01:32.958 --> 01:34.289
You want me to book them?

01:34.460 --> 01:35.792
- Yes.
- Bye.

01:35.962 --> 01:39.332
- Separately or together?
- Yes. Ha, ha.

01:42.173 --> 01:44.233
- Good morning, Kalia.
- Hello.

01:44.410 --> 01:45.502
