Where are the figs?

15:04.364 --> 15:06.926
Excuse me, where are the figs?
Because I want some figs!

15:07.102 --> 15:09.037
Sweetie? Sweetie. Hi.

15:09.206 --> 15:10.538
- Hi. Hi.
- Hi.

15:10.708 --> 15:12.176
Hi.

15:12.344 --> 15:14.906
Okay, look, you're right, okay?
You did order figs.

15:15.081 --> 15:18.143
But, uh, everyone seems
to be loving the salad, right?

15:18.320 --> 15:20.813
- Anybody missing figs?
- The dressing is a panoply...

15:20.991 --> 15:23.358
...of flavors.
- It's really good salad.

15:24.697 --> 15:27.030
- A lot to recommend, this salad.
- Okay. Sorry.

15:27.201 --> 15:30.730
- There she is. All right, she's back.
- I'm sorry, everyone. I just...

15:30.908 --> 15:34.607
It's my wedding and...
Well, I'm not usually a massive bitch.

15:34.780 --> 15:37.147
- She kind of is.
- Ha, ha. Stop it.

15:37.317 --> 15:40.720
I just really want everything
to start out perfectly.

15:40.889 --> 15:43.825
I mean, I only plan on getting married
four or five times, tops.

15:43.995 --> 15:45.896
Oh, sweetie.

15:46.064 --> 15:47.658
Oh, which reminds me, Connor.

15:47.835 --> 15:50.703
Sandy and I wanted to know
if you would make a toast tomorrow.

15:50.872 --> 15:52.205
What?

15:52.976 --> 15:56.243
- Yeah. We'd like that.
- I know it's not really your thing...

15:56.415 --> 15:59.614
